I had been recommended teeth straightening all my life but only after my husband went through a tooth extraction with Dr Abhilash is when I found someone completely trustworthy. I got my braces at his clinic even though it is a bit far for me and I have multiple options at walking distance from my home. Recently when my 5 year old needed some fillings, we went to Dr Abhilash again. It was such a smooth process because even my daughter trusted him and formed a bond with him, all because of his calm, soothing and friendly manner. I keep recommending him to everyone I know and I would highly recommend him to anyone who is looking for any kind of dental/maxillofacial treatment. Even if you have to travel a bit, it is completely worth!
